name: Vault Series Miami Bitcoin Hat 1st Edition
description: This limited run of 50 Vault Series Bitcoin hats starts the series with a Miami Style Bitcoin hat. The holder of this NFT will be airdropped another NFT on October 31 which will include a code for a free hat. On December 1, holder of this NFT will be airdropped NFT coupon for 10% lifetime discount on knowcrypto.today.
